The evidence with the title 'Here's how many Americans have nothing at all in savings ' says Jun 19, 2017  ... More people than you may think have absolutely nothing put away .  ... Half of all Americans have nothing put away for retirement and the vast majority of them  ... The U.S. have only several hundred dollars in their savings accounts and 34 percent have zero . Only 15 percent have over $10,000 stashed away. 
